{
  "texts": [
    "This assessment utilized a total of 1500 test data points, with 500 data points allocated to each digit.",
    "Hardware implementation for MNIST-digit classification.",
    "The singlelayer NN was trained using preprocessed MNIST digits with a softwarebased training method.",
    "The weight values of the trained network were derived by mapping analog values between binary 0 and 1.",
    "These resulting weights for each cell in the Crossbar Array (CA) were analog values ranging between 0 and 1."
  ]
}